				<p class="text-gray-600">
					In today's market, Health and Safety programs require more than just effectiveness; 
					they require an environment that consistently delivers desired outcomes. Element Safety 
					is the solution for efficient planning and valuable resources that aim to minimize 
					the severity of incidents and ultimately eliminate injuries that impact your business.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Experienced Consultants -->
			<div class="text-center">
				<div class="bg-green-100 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
					<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
