				<p class="text-gray-600">
					Element Safety is committed to delivering a comprehensive Environmental Health and 
					Safety Program that encompasses all relevant factors. Our experienced team has a 
					proven track record of effectively managing industry-leading EHS programs, achieving 
					exceptional outcomes.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Core Competencies -->
			<div class="text-center">
				<div class="bg-orange-100 w-20 h-20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-6">
					<svg class="w-10 h-10 text-orange-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
