				<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Core Competencies</h3>
				<p class="text-gray-600">
					Element Safety provides full service Environmental Health & Safety consulting. 
					These services include Construction Project Safety Support, EHS Augmentation, 
					EHS Program Development and Implementation, EHS Auditing, Incident Investigation, 
					and Industrial Hygiene consulting.
				</p>
